: : Wolfenstein/SharpClaw : :

Wolfenstein thinks about his situation a moment before he replies.

Wolfenstein: I will return to the Predacon ranks and prove my worth in combat.

Just then SharpClaw steps out into view, in his jaguar form.

SharpClaw: So you&#39;re a Predacon traitor, huh? You should feel lucky to be given this second chance.

Wolf sneers at the jaguar.

Wolfenstein: And may I ask who you are?

SharpClaw: The name is SharpClaw. I was heading back to the Predacon base myself, when I overheard you. Now I suggest you wipe that smirk off your face if you really want to return. I could also leave you here as spare parts.

Wolfenstein looks visably angered, but he decides that he should let it slide at this point.

Wolfenstein: Ok, then shut up and lets go. Beast mode.

Wolfenstein transforms to wolf mode.

SharpClaw (via commlink): Perceptor, it&#39;s SharpClaw. I&#39;m coming back to base and I&#39;m bringing this traitor with me.

The two Predacons walk off in the direction of the Predacon base.


